Path: `salons/{salonId}/employees/{employeeId}` — model: `lib/features/employees/data/models/employee.dart`.

## Fields

id: string (same as `{employeeId}` in path)
salonId: string
uid: string (optional — links to `users/{uid}` when provisioned)
name: string
email: string
phone: string (optional)
role: string (owner | admin | barber)
payrollPeriodOverride: string (optional — monthly | weekly; null = inherit salon `defaultPayrollPeriod`)
commissionRate: number
hourlyRate: number
isActive: boolean
createdAt: timestamp
updatedAt: timestamp

